  "text": "Step 5. Calculate the distances d(PLA i , PLPIS) and d(PLA i , PLNIS) of each alternative by Equations (14)- [CITATION_1] , respectively (Table 9 ): Step 6. Calculating the PLRCD of each alternative from PLPIS by Equation (18) ( Table 10 ). Step 7. According to the PLRCD(PLA i , PLPIS)(i = 1, 2, 3, 4, 5), we can rank all the suppliers of new agricultural machinery products. Obviously, the rank is A 3 > A 1 > A 4 > A 5 > A 2 and the best supplier among five alternatives is A 3 .",
